chat.cleanup.failure.description: There are currently no Herobrines loaded in this world!
chat.cleanup.fake.description: There is a fake Herobrine being displayed! Please remove it using the function fromthefog:admin/fake_herobrine/remove
This command activates the creeping mechanic and spawns Herobrine behind the player it is executed on.
chat.sighting_summons.lurking.tutorial.d: This command activates the lurking mechanic and spawns Herobrine somewhere off in the distance around the player it is executed on. Herobrine may not spawn if his spawnpoint is determined to be within 40 blocks of a player.
chat.sighting_summons.nightmare.tutorial: This command activates the nightmare mechanic and spawns Herobrine at the foot of the bed of the player it is executed on. Herobrine will not spawn if the player isn't in a bed.
This command activates the stalking mechanic and spawns Herobrine somewhere around the player it is executed on. Herobrine may not spawn if his spawnpoint is determined to be in the line of sight another player.
chat.sighting_summons.summon.tutorial.de: This command summons a Herobrine at the position of execution. Recommended for the executor to turn into spectator. A non-spectator player must be within radius.
config.OGshrineMechanic.description: Toggles whether or not lightning strikes when activating a Herobrine shrine.
config.OGshrineMechanic.title: OG Shrine Mechanic
config.advancements.description: Changes whether players will be rewarded advancements related to From The Fog. (ADVANCEMENTS GRANTED WHILE ENABLED WILL BE LOST IF DISABLED!!!)
config.advancements.title: Advancements
config.autoConfig.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine can modify the config.
config.autoConfig.title: Give It Control
config.burningBase.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will try to burn down your house once you leave the area (one check per in-game day).
config.burningBase.title: Burning Base
config.chilledCandles.description: Toggles whether or not Herobrine has the ability to snuff out the players candles.
config.chilledCandles.title: Chilled Candles
config.crashMechanic.description: Swaps the jumpscare mechanic for the og crash mechanic. [EPILEPSY WARNING!] [NOT FIT FOR WEAKER MACHINES!] (Only works when jumpscare is enabled.)
config.crashMechanic.title: Crash Mechanic
config.crashScreen.title: Crash Screen
config.crashScreenLibrary.screens.title: Crash Screens
config.creepingMechanic.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will stand behind you waiting for you to turn around.
config.creepingMechanic.title: Creeping Mechanic
config.creepingVanishingDelay.descriptio: Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught creeping up on the player.
config.creepingVanishingDelay.title: Creeping Vanishing Delay
config.crimsonCurse.description: Toggles whether or not Herobrine will change your torches to redstone torches and your lanterns to soul lanterns. (one check per in-game day)
config.crimsonCurse.title: Crimson Curse
config.disappearingTorches.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will try to break your torches once you leave the area (one check per in-game day).
config.disappearingTorches.title: Disappearing Torches
config.dreadfulDonation.description: Toggles whether or not Herobrine will leave you gifts in your chests. (Can happen before the 3 days pass or a shrine is built. One check per in-game day.)
config.dreadfulDonation.title: Dreadful Donation
config.emissiveLayers.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will have emissive layers. Useful for players who want to make him more vanilla, or that use dynamic lighting.
config.emissiveLayers.title: Emissive Layers
config.fearfulFootsteps.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will run up behind players creating footsteps.
config.fearfulFootsteps.title: Fearful Footsteps
config.ghostDoors.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine can open your doors.
config.ghostDoors.title: Ghost Doors
config.ghostMinecarts.description: Allows minecarts to move on their own, stay off the tracks. (one check per in-game day)
config.ghostMinecarts.title: Ghost Minecarts
config.ghostMiner.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will mine next to you in strip mines.
config.ghostMiner.title: Ghost Miner
config.hauntingDelay.description: Changes the delay for how long it takes for Herobrine to start major haunting (in-game days).
config.hauntingDelay.title: Haunting Delay
config.herobrineSkin.title: Herobrine Skin
config.hittingThatGriddyConfig.descripti: Changes whether or not Herobrine will spawn doing the griddy.
config.hittingThatGriddyConfig.title: Hitting That Griddy
config.hoeBrineReturnsConfig.description: Changes Herobrine back to Hoebrine as a reference to the original bug that would occur when the player would see Herobrine without the resourcepack enabled.
config.hoeBrineReturnsConfig.title: Hoebrine Returns
config.jumpscareMechanic.description: Enables the ability for Herobrine to jumpscare the player when they get too close.
config.jumpscareMechanic.title: Jumpscare Mechanic
config.lurkingLanguage.description: Changes the language that Herobrine will use to communicate with the player.
config.lurkingLanguage.title: Lurking Language
config.lurkingMechanic.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine will lurk around the player lunareclipse.watching from a very far distance.

config.lurkingVanishingDelay.description: Changes how long it takes for Herobrine to disappear after being caught lurking around the player.
config.lurkingVanishingDelay.title: Lurking Vanishing Delay
config.musicCut.description: Changes whether or not your music will suddenly stop playing when you spot Herobrine.

config.nameTag.description: Changes whether or not Herobrine has a nametag and how it appears.

config.nightmareMechanic.title: Nightmare Mechanic
config.noSleep.description: Toggles whether or not Herobrine will prevent you from sleeping when he's nearby. (Will not work on peaceful.)
config.noSleep.title: No Sleep
